Last updated: 11.06.2025

This Privacy Policy explains how My AutoPoster Bot (“we,” “us,” “Service”) handles your information when you use our Service.

1. Information We Collect
User-Provided Data
• Content data you supply for posting (images, videos, captions, metadata).

Automatically Collected Data
• Technical data (IP address, device type, browser).
• Usage data (timestamps of actions, features used).

2. How We Use Your Information
Service Provision
To publish your content on social platforms as instructed.

Analytics & Improvement
To analyze usage trends, diagnose issues, and improve the Service.

Notifications
To send you important service-related messages and alerts.

3. Data Sharing & Disclosure
Third-Party Platforms
We transmit only the content you authorize (e.g. to TikTok, Instagram, Telegram) to perform the posting.

Service Providers
We may share anonymized logs or metrics with hosting and analytics vendors under strict confidentiality.

Legal Requirements
We may disclose data if required by law or to protect our rights and safety or that of others.

4. Data Retention
We keep your content and logs only as long as necessary to operate the Service or as required by law. You can request deletion of your data at any time; we will comply within 30 days, except as otherwise legally required.

5. Security
We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure.

6. Your Rights
Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to:

Access your personal data

Correct or update inaccurate information

Delete your data (“right to be forgotten”)

Restrict or object to processing

Data portability

To exercise these rights, email us at: laplas.rouse@gmail.com

7. Children’s Privacy
Our Service is not directed to children under 16. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.

8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post changes here and update the “Last updated” date. Your continued use of the Service constitutes acceptance.

Contact Us
For questions or concerns, write to laplas.rouse@gmail.com
